Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在发表  我的梦想也决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.03,0:24:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  墙壁和KISS
