Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:22.55,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为与你紧紧相连  我才能让自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.76,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,随风行走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:30.08,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,相信的力量  铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.55,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Believe your love
